---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Cloud Intelligence - Premium Software Engineering Excellence"
  description="Founded in 2020 by James Burgess and Kaitlyn Wilson, Cloud Intelligence is a boutique software engineering agency specializing in enterprise-grade solutions, AI integration, and cloud-native architectures."
  keywords="about cloud intelligence, software engineering agency, James Burgess, boutique development, enterprise solutions, Cape Town software"
  
>
  <main class="about-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Cloud Intelligence</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Where software craftsmanship meets business transformation</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Story -->
    <section class="company-story">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="story-content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2020 by <strong>James Burgess (CEO/Lead Architect)</strong> and <strong>Kaitlyn Wilson (COO)</strong>, Cloud Intelligence emerged from a simple yet powerful vision: to build an amazing software shop known for making the highest quality products in the world.</p>
          
          <p>Based in Cape Town, South Africa, we operate as a remote-first company that has grown into a boutique software engineering agency specializing in high-quality, enterprise-grade solutions. Our focus areas include data engineering, web applications, and AI integration – technologies that are reshaping how businesses operate in the digital age.</p>

          <p>What started as a two-person partnership has evolved into a carefully curated team of 8 elite professionals, each bringing exceptional skills and an unwavering commitment to excellence. We've maintained our boutique approach, ensuring every project receives the attention and craftsmanship it deserves.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission & Values -->
    <section class="mission-values">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="mission-grid">
          <div class="mission-card">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>"To build an amazing software shop known for making the highest quality products in the world."</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="values-card">
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Correctness:</strong> Things must be done correctly, no exceptions</li>
              <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Highest standard quality in all deliverables</li>
              <li><strong>Value:</strong> Every action must extract business value</li>
              <li><strong>Craftsmanship:</strong> Approaching software development as an art form</li>
              <li><strong>Systems Thinking:</strong> Understanding and simplifying complex systems</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Stats -->
    <section class="company-stats">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Impact</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">8TB+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Daily data processed via customer pipelines</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">1M+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Users trust our platforms globally</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Countries where our applications operate</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">$400M+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Processed & audited through our systems</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Approach -->
    <section class="our-approach">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="approach-content">
          <p>Our philosophy centers around "<strong>Quality &lt; Value</strong>" – extracting value from the first keystroke while maintaining the highest quality standards. We believe in treating software development as an art form, where every line of code reflects our commitment to excellence.</p>

          <div class="approach-pillars">
            <div class="pillar">
              <h4>Craftsman Philosophy</h4>
              <p>Deep love and appreciation for the art of building with software, ensuring every deliverable represents a masterpiece of engineering excellence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
              <h4>Systems Thinking</h4>
              <p>Exceptional ability to understand complex systems and break them into simple, manageable components that scale effortlessly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
              <h4>Value Engineering</h4>
              <p>Identifying exactly what needs to be built and how to build it for maximum value extraction and business impact.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technology Expertise -->
    <section class="tech-expertise">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
        <div class="tech-grid">
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h4>Core Technologies</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Python (primary), language-agnostic approach</li>
              <li>Django + Vue.js + Kubernetes + PostgreSQL</li>
              <li>Cloud-native architectures (GCP certified)</li>
              <li>AI/ML integration and generative AI</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h4>Specialized Skills</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Complex systems architecture</li>
              <li>Custom ETL pipeline design</li>
              <li>Business intelligence and analytics</li>
              <li>Enterprise integration solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team CTA -->
    <section class="team-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Meet Our Leadership</h2>
          <p>Led by visionary architects and supported by elite professionals, our team combines technical brilliance with strategic business insight.</p>
          <a href="/webtest/team" class="cta-button">Meet the Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Growth Strategy -->
    <section class="growth-strategy">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Looking Forward</h2>
        <p>As we continue to grow, our focus remains on three key areas: building professional presence through case studies and partnerships, expanding our analytics services with weekly public data dashboards, and launching our proprietary AI chat application to demonstrate our capabilities to potential clients.</p>
        
        <p>We maintain our boutique approach while scaling strategically, adding specialists as new clients require and leveraging our reliable network of elite developers.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .about-page {
    padding-top: 80px; // Account for fixed navbar
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  // Hero Section
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3366FF 0%, #2952CC 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      text-align: center;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  // Company Story
  .company-story {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #FFFFFF;

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .story-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      
      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: #4a4a4a;
      }
    }
  }

  // Mission & Values
  .mission-values {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;

    .mission-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 30px;
      }
    }

    .mission-card, .values-card {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

      h3 {
        font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #3366FF;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4a4a4a;
        font-style: italic;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;

        li {
          margin-bottom: 16px;
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
          color: #4a4a4a;

          strong {
            color: #3366FF;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  // Company Stats
  .company-stats {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: white;

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .stat-item {
      text-align: center;

      .stat-number {
        font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #3366FF;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .stat-label {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #b3b3b3;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
    }
  }

  // Our Approach
  .our-approach, .growth-strategy {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .approach-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;

      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        color: #4a4a4a;
      }
    }

    .approach-pillars {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 40px;

      .pillar {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #3366FF;

        h4 {
          font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
          color: #3366FF;
        }

        p {
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
          color: #4a4a4a;
          margin: 0;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  // Technology Expertise
  .tech-expertise {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .tech-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .tech-category {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

      h4 {
        font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #3366FF;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;

        li {
          margin-bottom: 12px;
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: 1.5;
          color: #4a4a4a;
          padding-left: 20px;
          position: relative;

          &:before {
            content: "→";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #3366FF;
            font-weight: bold;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  // Team CTA
  .team-cta {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3366FF 0%, #2952CC 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: #3366FF;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;

      &:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      }
    }
  }

  // Growth Strategy
  .growth-strategy {
    p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4a4a4a;
    }
  }
</style>
